data.description: Special Offer: We are providing a $7,800 2-1 buydown. Discover this adorable duplex nestled in the Ridge Run Subdivision. Boasting a comfortable layout with 3 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom (with a rough-in for an additional bathroom in the future), this home is designed for both functionality and charm. Step inside to find a separate dining area and a spacious living room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for daily living. The partially finished basement adds additional potential for expansion or customization, allowing you to shape the space according to your needs. The back yard is nicely fenced, updated and offering privacy and a perfect area for outdoor gatherings and entertaining. With new interior paint and a new roof installed in 2023, this home is not only charming but also updated and move-in ready. An appealing feature is the absence of a HOA, providing greater flexibility and freedom in homeownership.Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours-call to schedule your personal showing today!
